      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not suitable for daily driving without major repairs. It suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a slipping transmission and a persistent engine knock, alongside visible frame rust and body damage. The interior is heavily worn with several non-functional components and torn seating. This car is ideal for a dedicated restoration enthusiast or as a donor for parts.",
