    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a concours-level example of mid-engine precision. Powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, it delivers linear power delivery and visceral feedback. The chassis features PASM active damping and monobloc four-piston calipers for exceptional lateral grip and deceleration. Meticulously preserved with a documented IMS solution, zero over-revs on the ECU log, and a flawless underbody, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of the analog driving experience. Recent service includes comprehensive fluid analysis and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires.",
      "price": 46500.0,
